</tr><tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">©David Valdés</td></tr></tbody></table><div style="text-align: justify;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: justify;">Los tornillos que sujetan las bellotas...,</div><br /><br /><table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qL2sTe1Gb34/VZhPtXFL3fI/AAAAAAAACvQ/qoSZn6wm9Mc/s1600/tornillos%2Bbellotas.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"><img border="0" height="400" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qL2sTe1Gb34/VZhPtXFL3fI/AAAAAAAACvQ/qoSZn6wm9Mc/s400/tornillos%2Bbellotas.JPG" width="250" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">©David Valdés </td></tr></tbody></table><br /><br /><table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_xnUeLrumDg/VZhPMM2M3rI/AAAAAAAACvM/N65rDQRJOD0/s1600/tornillos%2Bbellotas%2B2.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"><img border="0" height="400" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_xnUeLrumDg/VZhPMM2M3rI/AAAAAAAACvM/N65rDQRJOD0/s400/tornillos%2Bbellotas%2B2.JPG" width="270" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">©David Valdés </td></tr></tbody></table><br /><br /><div style="text-align: justify;">Los tornillos de la bordonera..., </div><br /><br /><table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-UyklI7LraVk/VYfUbac39nI/AAAAAAAACtM/ryTZ1JaahWY/s1600/tornillos%2Bbord%25C3%25B3n%2B1.JPG" imageanchor=